      "content": "This intense feeling of guilt is incredibly painful, but existing in your brain does not mean you are a poison that must be removed just to love your children better. You are clearly trying to protect them by withdrawing, yet the.distance you mistake itself as protection could actually isolate them or cause them more confusion. Please seek immediate professional support to help navigate these complex thoughts so you can process your mistakes without believing they define your worth as a parent.",
